name: Little Oddy Space Suit Fett Ver.
description:
This work as an issue for my next art toy release. Tells what if Oddy enters the Star Wars universe. On the planet Mandalore, he trains and gets armor like Boba Fett who will go on a mission as a bounty hunter.

I really love the comic cover art. Often, in art toy releases, I make issues with this type of work. With the intention of being a cover, or entrance to every theme created. For this fett edition, the toy version will be released in december via my bigcartel website. check my instagram @iky.z if you want to know information about the toy version.
